### Phase 6: Wire up `__complete` in bin.ts

**File: `src/bin.ts`** — Add fast-path at the very top of `main()`:

```typescript
async function main(): Promise<void> {
  const args = process.argv.slice(2);

  // Fast-path: shell completion (no telemetry, no middleware)
  if (args[0] === "__complete") {
    const { handleComplete } = await import("./lib/complete.js");
    await handleComplete(args.slice(1));
    return;
  }

  // ... rest of main() unchanged
}
```

Key: use dynamic `import()` so the completion module isn't loaded on normal CLI runs.

